from typing import List, Union
from accessor import getValue, setValue

video_1_url ='https://assets-global.website-files.com/612770618d97595db63a9470/63ac3b9bfdf77f2d66802200_Query%20and%20debug-transcode.mp4'
video_2_url = 'https://assets-global.website-files.com/612770618d97595db63a9470/64ad5cb7b1395cef0d37b115_LLM%20Comparison-transcode.mp4'

toggle = 1

def on_change_video_click(path: List[Union[str, int]]):
    global toggle
    if (toggle == 1):
        setValue(['video'], video_2_url)
        toggle = 2
    elif (toggle == 2):
        setValue(['video'], video_1_url)
        toggle = 1

    return
